        <title>抽象层次平缓提升的 Church Encoding</title>
        <link>http://fyshxfish.github.io/p/%E6%8A%BD%E8%B1%A1%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%B3%E7%BC%93%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E7%9A%84-church-encoding/</link>
